(	
    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

and d.menu_cd_path like '%' || 'MN_CM_4000' || '%'

order by d.ord asc

	,d.menu_kind

	,d.menu_nm

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)

d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd

	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path

00:09:06.082-[32mINFO [0;39m-jdbc.sqltiming - WITH RECURSIVE subdepartment AS
(	
    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd 
	,a.ord
	,a.pgm_id
	,a.rmk
	,a.menu_path
	,a.crt_dtm
	,a.updt_dtm
	,a.menu_cd::text as menu_cd_path
	FROM tb_cm_menu a 
	where a.prnt_menu_cd is null

    UNION ALL

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

and d.menu_cd_path like '%' || 'MN_CM_4000' || '%'

order by d.ord asc

		AND B.MENU_NO =A.MENU_NO
	)
	order by ord asc

00:09:17.488-[32mINFO [0;39m-jdbc.sqltiming - WITH RECURSIVE subdepartment AS
(	
    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd 
	,a.ord
	,a.pgm_id

	,a.updt_dtm
	,a.menu_cd::text as menu_cd_path
	FROM tb_cm_menu a 
	where a.prnt_menu_cd is null

    UNION ALL

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

and d.menu_kind = 'M'

order by d.ord asc

(	
    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd 
	,a.ord
	,a.pgm_id
	,a.rmk
	,a.menu_path
	,a.crt_dtm
	,a.updt_dtm
	,a.menu_cd::text as menu_cd_path
	FROM tb_cm_menu a 
	where a.prnt_menu_cd is null

    UNION ALL

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

order by d.ord asc

(	
    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd 
	,a.ord
	,a.pgm_id

	,a.menu_path

	,a.updt_dtm

	FROM tb_cm_menu a 
	where a.prnt_menu_cd is null

    UNION ALL

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

and d.menu_cd_path like '%' || 'MN_CM_4000' || '%'

order by d.ord asc

00:12:26.787-[32mINFO [0;39m-jdbc.sqltiming - WITH RECURSIVE subdepartment AS
(	
    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd 
	,a.ord
	,a.pgm_id
	,a.rmk
	,a.menu_path
	,a.crt_dtm
	,a.updt_dtm
	,a.menu_cd::text as menu_cd_path
	FROM tb_cm_menu a 
	where a.prnt_menu_cd is null

    UNION ALL

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

and d.menu_kind = 'M'

order by d.ord asc

    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd

	FROM tb_cm_menu a 
	where a.prnt_menu_cd is null

    UNION ALL

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

order by d.ord asc

    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)

d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd

	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path

    JOIN subdepartment sd

)

	,d.menu_cd

)

(	
    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd

	FROM tb_cm_menu a

    UNION ALL

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

and d.menu_cd_path like '%' || 'MN_CM_4000' || '%'

order by d.ord asc

(	
    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd 
	,a.ord

	,a.menu_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu a 
	where a.prnt_menu_cd is null

    UNION ALL

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

and d.menu_cd_path like '%' || 'MN_CM_4000' || '%'

order by d.ord asc

	,d.menu_nm

    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)

	,d.menu_cd

	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm

	,d.pgm_id

	,d.updt_dtm

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm

	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path

00:27:17.738-[32mINFO [0;39m-jdbc.sqltiming - WITH RECURSIVE subdepartment AS
(	
    -- non-recursive term
    SELECT a.menu_no
	,a.menu_cd
	,a.menu_kind
	,a.menu_lvl
	,a.menu_nm
	,a.prnt_menu_cd 
	,a.ord
	,a.pgm_id
	,a.rmk
	,a.menu_path
	,a.crt_dtm
	,a.updt_dtm
	,a.menu_cd::text as menu_cd_path
	FROM tb_cm_menu a 
	where a.prnt_menu_cd is null

    UNION ALL

    -- recursive term
    SELECT d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,sd.menu_cd_path ||'>'|| d.menu_cd as menu_cd_path

	FROM tb_cm_menu  d
    JOIN subdepartment sd 
	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)
select 
d.menu_no
	,d.menu_cd
	,d.menu_kind
	,d.menu_lvl
	,d.menu_nm
	,d.prnt_menu_cd 
	,d.ord
	,d.pgm_id
	,d.rmk
	,d.menu_path
	,d.crt_dtm
	,d.updt_dtm
	,d.menu_cd_path
from subdepartment d
where 1=1

and d.menu_kind = 'M'

order by d.ord asc

	ON (d.prnt_menu_cd = sd.menu_cd)
)

	,d.menu_cd_path

where 1=1

)
